GLANCE
Created by Serkan TEKIN
1/1 Edition
April 15, 2018 - Istanbul
5916x3328 300 dpi

Sometimes a glance can tell a lot us. It makes us wonder. Contains a mystery. As in this photo...

Where is she looking? 

This photo was taken in 1/640 of a second and captured the mystery of that moment in one frame.
